  "description": "Use when implementing or reviewing user feedback patterns in Lightning Web Components \u2014 specifically toast messages, lightning-alert, lightning-confirm, lightning-prompt, and platform notifications. Trigger keywords: 'ShowToastEvent', 'toast in lwc', 'lightning-alert lwc', 'lightning-confirm promise', 'Experience Cloud notification'. NOT for modal overlays (use lwc-modal-and-overlay).",
